{"_path":"/blog/zh/mdn_localization_tutorial","_dir":"zh","_draft":false,"_partial":false,"_locale":"","_empty":false,"title":"给 MDN 文档本地化参与新人的一些入门指导和经验分享","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h1","props":{"id":"给-mdn-文档本地化参与新人的一些入门指导和经验分享"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"给 MDN 文档本地化参与新人的一些入门指导和经验分享"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"mdn-文档介绍"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MDN 文档介绍"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://developer.mozilla.org/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MDN 文档"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，全称是 Mozilla Developer Docs（Mozilla 开发者文档，顺带一提火狐浏览器就是 Mozilla 家的），基本涵盖了前端开发的所有知识，可以说是前端开发学习必不可少的参考资料。"},{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"才怪，我就是看菜鸟教程入门的前端。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"mdn-文档的现状"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MDN 文档的现状"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"MDN 文档现在托管在 Github 上（所以说文档的本质是代码 (￣y▽,￣)╭ ），每一篇文章都是用 Markdown 写的（关于 Markdown 的入门介绍可以参看我的"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://hanyujie2002.fly.dev/blog/zh/an_introduce_to_markdown","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这篇文章"}]},{"type":"text","value":"）。所有人都可以通过 Git 这个工具来参与贡献。（不熟悉 Git？其实不用 Git 也可以贡献哦，后面介绍）MDN 文档在 Github 上主要分为两个部分，一个是 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/mdn/content","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Content 仓库"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，存储英文文档，还有一个是 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"translated-content 仓库"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，与 Content 仓库的结构基本相同，不过是存储翻译（更精确的术语，本地化）后的文档。Translated-content 仓库就是本文关注的重点啦。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"目前 MDN 文档的简体中文本地化还是很活跃的，差不多每天都有人提交新的翻译。但是还是很缺人手的。（以前我写代码比较英文文档和中文文档，发现有大约 8000 多篇文档没有被本地化 w(ﾟДﾟ)w，而且很多老文章质量有待提升）如果你能参与其中的话，会是对 MDN 本地化工作的极大帮助（I WANT YOU.jpg）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"MDN_本地化招聘海报","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/MDN_%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%8C%96%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98%E6%B5%B7%E6%8A%A5.jpg"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"如何给自己找任务"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何给自己找任务"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"入门级提升排版"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"入门级：提升排版"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"首先，入门级别的任务就是提升文档的排版，早期的 MDN（迁移到 Github 之前的）的一些本地化的文档的排版工作做的很不好，有很大的提升空间。关于文档排版方面要注意的点，"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/docs/zh-cn/translation-guide.md","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这篇文章"}]},{"type":"text","value":"里有详细的介绍，我挑几个重要的讲："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"标点符号：除了代码里的符号及一些特殊情况之外，其他地方都用中文（全角符号）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"中文和英文，中文和数字之间要有一个空格：传说盘古开天辟地，在天与地之间辟出了一片空白，故这个空格又名盘古之白（有一个专门搞排版的工具就叫盘古）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"不要将“you”翻译为“您”，MDN 是程序员写给程序员看的文档 "},{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"程序员有，程序员治，程序员享（By the programmers, for the programmers）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"，大家彼此平等也就不需要用敬辞了。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"英文单词不要用复数形式：比如说 APIs 翻译到中文之间翻译成 API 就行了。"},{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"你总不能翻译成“API 们”吧。"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这种排版问题真的随便翻一翻就能找到很多："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917214438","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917214438.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"比如这里就出现了汉字和字母之间没有空格的问题，这个时候肯定有同学就跃跃欲试地想要提交修改了，那么该怎么样提交呢？这里就教大家最简单的方法："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ol","props":{"start":0},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"解决网络问题："},{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这个对于大家应该都不难吧"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注册 Github 账号：注册账号的链接在这里 ┏ (゜ω゜)=☞ "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/signup","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"https://github.com/signup"}]}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917215204","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917215204.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"万恶之源"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注册完账号之后，再次回到要提交修改的那个 MDN 文章的页面上，来到文章底部，你会发现有个“Edit the page on GitHub”的链接，点击一下。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917215920","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917215920.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"之后，来到这个文档对应地 Github 页面（没错，MDN 页面的来源就是这里），开始对对应内容进行修改（没有修改的话，那个“Commit changes”按钮是灰的）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"修改完后，点击“Commit Changes”按钮（Commit Changes 就是提交修改的意思）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917220738","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917220738.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"之后，填一下 Commit message（关于提交的信息），这里最好用英文，为啥中文本地化贡献者都是中文用的很熟练的人，却要用英文咧？这是因为 MDN 是一个全球性的开源社区，里面的很多贡献者未必会中文，如果用英语的话，可以让其他语言的人也能参与进去。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917221050","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917221050.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"之后，点“Propose changes”按钮（还是提交修改的意思）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"之后来到 Comparing Changes 页面（比较修改页面），这个页面信息比较多，不要慌，这里其实很简单，就是以直观的方式显示你所作的修改（红色为原文，绿色为修改后的文章）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917221735","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917221735.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"之后点击那个“Create pull request”按钮（pull request，简称 PR，就是拉取请求的意思，可以理解为请求拥有仓库（这里是 MDN 文档）管理权限的管理员接受你对代码（这里是文档）的修改）。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"之后，来到“Open a pull request”页面。（创建一个拉取请求）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917222626","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917222626.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"最后一步了！"},{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"激不激动"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"这里简单地填一下信息就行了。依然是最好用英文填。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917223203","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917223203.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意这里我在标题那里标了一个“zh-CN”前缀，这是干啥用的捏？记得我前面说的吗？MDN 是个全球社群，你看这个“Pull Request”列表里就有“ko”（Korea，韩文）、“zh”（中文）、“ja”（日语）和“fr”（法语），标一个语言前缀可以方便辨认具体是来自哪个语言的 Pull Request。"},{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"其实你不标，MDN 的 bot 也会自动给你打上语言标签的啦（在每个 PR 标题的后面）。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917223407","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917223407.png"},"children":[]},{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"万国来朝"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917223203","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917223203.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"回到正题，这里“same as title”就是同标题的意思，下面哪个“ditto”是啥意思呢？“ditto”来自于托斯卡纳方言，可以追溯道意大利语的“detto”，再往上可以追溯到拉丁文的“said”，就是“一样（在这里是和上文一样）”的意思，这个也是我从 MDN 的另一个本地化贡献者 "},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://github.com/JasonLamv-t","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"@JasonLamv-t"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 大佬那里学到的😁。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"之后，点击“create pull request”按钮。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"img","props":{"alt":"20230917224955","src":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/hanyujie2002/my_pictures/images/20230917224955.png"},"children":[]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"到此任务就完成了，接下来等 MDN 的管理员来处理你的 Pull Request 并拉取就可以啦。"},{"type":"element","tag":"del","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"才怪，管理员给建议之后，你要按建议改才行"}]},{"type":"text","value":" 等你的修改被接受（专业术语，merge）之后，过一段时间，你就可以在那篇 MDN 文档那里看到你的修改了，当然 Github 的那篇文章的 commit history（提交历史）上也永远地留下了你的足迹！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h3","props":{"id":"进阶级翻译整篇文章nanna"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"进阶级：翻译整篇文章nanna"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"todo：创建文件教程"}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"mdn-文档介绍","depth":2,"text":"MDN 文档介绍"},{"id":"mdn-文档的现状","depth":2,"text":"MDN 文档的现状"},{"id":"如何给自己找任务","depth":2,"text":"如何给自己找任务","children":[{"id":"入门级提升排版","depth":3,"text":"入门级：提升排版"},{"id":"进阶级翻译整篇文章nanna","depth":3,"text":"进阶级：翻译整篇文章nanna"}]}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:blog:zh:2.MDN_localization_tutorial.md","_source":"content","_file":"blog/zh/2.MDN_localization_tutorial.md","_extension":"md"}